-- Villagers in Southern China Protest Pollution From Smelter, News Reports
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-14T04:16:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-14/villagers-in-southern-china-protest-pollution-from-smelter-news-reports.html

          
          
             Hundreds of Chinese villagers in the
southern region of Guangxi protested pollution from an aluminum
smelter, the China News Service reported, citing a local
government press office.  
